div.p:
Consecutive usage of this slash stops at the end of 18Rb; 47Rb also contains lines with
          the divider as do occasional lines throughout the manuscript, with no evident plan (47Rb;
          53Va; 62V- 63R; 72Ra; 73Vb; 84V).

